Introduction

LUMINOUS was a four-member boy group under Bareunson WIP. The members consisted of Woobin, Steven, Suil, and Youngbin. They made their debut on September 9th, 2021 with the mini album "YOUTH".

SEG Entertainment made an announcement on September 6, 2024, through Luminous' official accounts, that there were internal conflicts going on which prohibited Luminous from meeting fans. In the announcement it stated that Luminous would be transferring to a new company and starting anew. On February 9, 2025, it was announced that all members of LUMINOUS had terminated their contracts as well as activites, and would consequently be disbanding.
